<p>Check your <a href="/blog/content-marketing-statistics/">content marketing statistics</a> benchmarks to understand where your industry stands. A 40% open rate might be excellent for B2B software but below average for a local service business.</p>
<p><strong>Why this step matters:</strong> Welcome sequences that never get updated decay over time. What worked 6 months ago might underperform today. Regular optimization keeps your sequence competitive.</p>
